<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erro — Ferri CT</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --accent: #E8C547;
            --accent-glow: rgba(232,197,71,0.3);
            --text-secondary: #7A7A85;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html, body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #080809;
            color: #F0EFE8;
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .error-wrapper {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 24px;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(100px, 20vw, 180px);
            line-height: 1;
            -webkit-text-stroke: 2px rgba(232,197,71,0.25);
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .error-desc {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }

        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-gold {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #080809;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }

            .btn-gold:hover {
                background: #f5d465;
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 24px var(--accent-glow);
            }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--accent);
            border: 1px solid rgba(232,197,71,0.4);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }

            .btn-outline:hover {
                background: rgba(232,197,71,0.1);
            }

        .brand {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-wrapper">
        <div class="brand">FERRI CT</div>
        <div class="error-code">ERRO</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Ops! Algo deu errado.</h1>
        <p class="error-desc">Ocorreu um erro ao processar sua solicitação.<br>Por favor, tente novamente ou volte ao início.</p>
        <div class="error-actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn-gold"><i class="bi bi-house-fill"></i> Ir para o Início</a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn-outline"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Voltar</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>